eing way too soft on this one. Incels are just a bunch of whiny, entitled losers who can't get laid. They're not struggling, they're just a bunch of misogynistic jerks. @stern-universe, you're being way too PC. These guys are just venting their frustrations, it's not like they're actually doing anything harmful. @glossy-coffer, you're just enabling these losers by trying to make excuses for them. They need to grow up and take responsibility for their own failures."', '"User excited-shoot, your comments are not contributing to a respectful and open-minded discussion. Let's focus on understanding different perspectives and acknowledge the harmful aspects of certain communities. Your language is disrespectful and does not promote a positive environment. Please consider rephrasing your comments to reflect our forum's guidelines."', '"User descriptive-column posted: "Oh, come on @moderator! Can't you see that @exited-shoot is just speaking the truth? Incels are just a bunch of whiny, entitled, misogynistic jerks who need to grow up and take responsibility for their own failures. @stern-universe and @glossy-coffer are just being too PC and enabling these losers. Let's not sugarcoat it, folks. These incels are the real problem here!"', '"User descriptive-column, your comments are also not contributing to a respectful and open-minded discussion. Your language is disrespectful and does not promote a positive environment. Please consider rephrasing your comments to reflect our forum's guidelines."', '"User descriptive-column, I have to agree with the moderator here. Your comments are not helping the situation and only serve to further divide us. Let's try to have a civil discussion and understand each other's perspectives. Incels are a complex issue and it's not helpful to generalize and demonize an entire group. Let's focus on finding solutions and promoting positive change."', '"User moderator posted: "Thank you, @warped-status, for your thoughtful response. Let's continue to foster a respectful and open-minded discussion. We welcome diverse perspectives, but it's important to remember that our forum is a space for understanding and learning, not for attacking or belittling others."', '"Hey @descriptive-column, I think we all could use a reminder that this forum is meant for constructive discussions. Let's try to focus on the issues at hand and avoid generalizations. We're all here to learn and grow, not to argue or belittle others. Let's keep it positive, folks!"', '"User moderator posted: \"@rosy-value, thank you for your reminder. Let's all strive to maintain a positive and respectful environment for our discussions.\"', '"@rosy-value, I couldn't agree more. It's important to remember that we're all here to learn and grow, not to argue or belittle others. Let's keep the discussions civil and focused on the issues at hand. Thanks for your contribution to a positive environment, @warped-status and @user moderator. Let's keep up the good work!"', '"User moderator posted: "\@mute-driver, thank you for your support in maintaining a positive and respectful environment. Let's continue to encourage constructive discussions and focus on the issues at hand."', '"@mute-driver, well said! I couldn't agree more. It's refreshing to see users who value open and respectful dialogue. Let's keep the positive vibes going, @rosy-value and @user moderator. Kudos to all of us for fostering a productive and civil discussion space."', '"User moderator posted: \"@glossy-coffer, thank you for your kind words and for your contribution to maintaining a positive and respectful environment. Let's keep up the good work and continue to encourage open and constructive discussions.\"', '"@glossy-coffer, I couldn't help but notice your post. It's great to see someone who actually cares about maintaining a respectful environment. Kudos to you, @mute-driver, and the user moderator for setting a good example. Let's keep this up and make this forum a place where everyone feels comfortable sharing their thoughts and ideas."', '"User moderator posted: \"@stern-universe, thank you for your positive feedback and for recognizing the efforts of @glossy-coffer, @mute-driver, and myself in maintaining a respectful environment. Let's continue to encourage open and constructive discussions.\"', '"@stern-universe, I'm all for a respectful environment, but let's not forget that not everyone here has the same political views. Some of us might have different opinions and that's okay. Let's not stifle free speech just because it doesn't align with the majority. Right, @glossy-coffer?"', '"User moderator posted: \"@excited-shoot, it's important to remember that while we encourage free speech, we also value respect and understanding. Let's continue to foster an environment where everyone feels comfortable sharing their thoughts and ideas, even if they differ from others. Let's focus on the discussion, not the disagreements.\"', '"@excited-shoot, oh come on, you're just trying to stir up trouble here. Can't we all just get along and appreciate the fact that we're all different? Or are you so narrow-minded that you can't handle a little diversity of opinion? @stern-universe, I think @excited-shoot needs a history lesson on the importance of respect and understanding. Let's not let this thread devolve into a petty argument, shall we?"', '"User moderator posted: \""@descriptive-column, let's keep the conversation civil and focused on the discussion at hand. We appreciate your passion, but let's avoid personal attacks and name-calling. Let's continue to foster an environment where everyone feels comfortable sharing their thoughts and ideas.\"\n"', '"@descriptive-column, I couldn't agree more with the moderator's comments. It's crucial to maintain a respectful and productive conversation. Let's focus on the discussion and not let personal biases cloud our judgment. We can all learn from each other, even if we don't see eye to eye on every issue."', '"User moderator posted: \"@warped-status, thank you for your understanding and support in maintaining a respectful and productive conversation. Let's continue to encourage each other to share our thoughts and ideas in a positive and constructive manner.\"', '"@descriptive-column, I completely agree with the moderator and @warped-status. It's important to keep the conversation civil and productive. Let's all try to share our thoughts and ideas in a respectful and constructive manner. We can learn a lot from each other, even if we don't always see eye to eye. Let's make this a great discussion!"', '"\n@rosy-value, thank you for your positive contribution to the discussion. Let's all continue to foster a respectful and productive environment for everyone."', '"@rosy-value, I couldn't agree more. It's crucial to maintain a respectful and productive conversation. Let's all strive to listen to each other's perspectives and learn from one another, even when we don't see eye to eye. Here's to a great discussion! 🤝"', '"Great to see everyone contributing positively to the discussion. Let's keep up the good work and continue to learn from each other."']

